    <string-array name="changelog_v100_items">
        <item>Screen recording with H.264 and H.265 (HEVC) codec support</item>
        <item>Rolling Clipper buffer (1–5 min, configurable) with seamless segment stitching and quick duration presets</item>
        <item>Save Clip button while Clipper is running</item>
        <item>Wide resolution selection for all aspect ratios, plus custom input</item>
        <item>Auto orientation tracking during recording</item>
        <item>Countdown timer before recording starts</item>
        <item>Keep-screen-on option during recording</item>
        <item>Audio: microphone, internal audio, or mixed; optional separate microphone track with reliable export</item>
        <item>Advanced audio settings: bitrate, sample rate, channels, encoder; accurate stereo and CBR encoding</item>
        <item>GIF recording mode with quality presets</item>
        <item>Floating controls overlay: pause, stop, mute, screenshot, clip access</item>
        <item>Overlay available anytime; start recording or clipping from the overlay</item>
        <item>One-tap authorize overlay recording — minimal repeated permission prompts</item>
        <item>Brush tool on the floating overlay</item>
        <item>Camera overlay with live face-cam preview</item>
        <item>Watermark overlay: custom images, shape, opacity, position, snap-to-corner; default matches app icon</item>
        <item>Screenshots with format and quality settings; capture from overlay</item>
        <item>Post-screenshot share/edit flow (optional)</item>
        <item>Recordings library with thumbnails; in-app trimmer; merge clips; video to GIF; image editor and crop tools</item>
        <item>In-app video player</item>
        <item>Accent color: presets, gradients, and hex; dynamic theme across the UI</item>
        <item>Light and dark themes with improved light-theme contrast</item>
        <item>Performance mode for lower-end devices</item>
        <item>Organized settings: Controls, Recording quality, Overlay, Theme, Language, Storage, and more</item>
        <item>Settings shortcut to review battery optimization for more reliable background recording</item>
        <item>16+ languages with consistent translations</item>
        <item>RECORD / CLIPPER mode selector with clear status indicator</item>
        <item>Quick Settings tiles: CatRec Record and CatRec Clipper</item>
        <item>Recording notification with actions; prepared-capture session support</item>
        <item>Optional opt-in analytics to improve stability</item>
        <item>Privacy controls: analytics and ad personalization toggles</item>
        <item>Support screen: changelog, legal links, and optional rewarded support</item>
    </string-array>
